                    int validity,
                    IsamiVersion isamiVersion,
                    IsamiSubVersion isamiSubVersion,
                    boolean applyCompression)
        Creates ISAMI fast equivalent stress analysis process.
        Parameters:
        task - The owner task of this process.
        sequenceFile - Path to input stress sequence file. This can be either SIGMA or STH file.
        material - Material.
        keepOutputs - True to keep analysis output files.
        outputFileName - Output file name. This will be used only if the analysis output file is kept.
        anaFileID - ANA file ID.
        flsFileID - FLS file ID.
        validity - Spectrum validity.
        isamiVersion - ISAMI version.
        isamiSubVersion - ISAMI sub version.
        applyCompression - True compression should be applied in propagation analysis.
